name: Nena Trampa N.6
description: Immortal and powerful, I hold the world and your life in my hands. The delicious elixir that flows in your veins seduces me, if you let me get close I will make you feel the most special person of all your lives. When I place my lips on your skin and you enter my body, we will be one. I promise it won't hurt, I promise we'll be eternal, I promise sweet torture.
